Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三話 尋找面碼會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那我去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說我呢 老爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不過還是不說好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...還不如說我...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 仁太 怎麼能不去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有謝anaru啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校 記得來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還幫你一起玩口袋妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話不算數要打手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 說不定這就是面碼的願望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望仁太能去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是這樣啊  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我換衣服 你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.66,0:01:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出各種莫名其妙要求的夏天的猛獸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 也許...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要實現願望吧 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看日期應該已經是初秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的猛獸依然盤踞在我家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我趕出家門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無選擇...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬 蟬 人 蟬 汗 汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗 汗 太陽 汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 人 視線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊 學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是因為你讓我來我才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起 來學校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀 春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鳴子 還有宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 沒事的 才一個學期不來而已沒人會在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 也沒人把宿海放在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 別太...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 愛的力量還真是偉大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你去了他家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛 火熱的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說了 誰會對這種傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是熱昏了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會想要來這種全都是低能兒的動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁...宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還是要回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那 剛才那莫非就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在逞強?  -不是吧 那也算?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看家...好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太家大冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這邊的房間是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太的媽媽去世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母可是比這相片看著要漂亮多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼的照片也是 其實我不是很喜歡那照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過面碼拍照片的時候總是V
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不V照片基本上沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然面碼也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過面碼現在還好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又哭了 仁太會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:27.50,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(狗不要放養)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和anaru之間的約定無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為面碼 我的幻想讓我去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 仁太 怎麼能不去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不了家了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bentora bentota space people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 搭檔!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭檔?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看見了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了?看見什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-還用問嗎 面碼啊  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:20.82,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我還真是越來越強大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我的幻想會...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 應該是奇蹟般的時機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小便 像這樣 劃出了一道奇蹟的弧線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這時 我想應該是Δ的形狀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.28,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(這裡的希臘字母Δ和出來了的讀音一樣 冷笑話)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那應該是看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?不會不會  我視力可是Ousmane級別的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:40.11,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Ousmane Sankhon 此人視力6.0)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼 真是長大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長...長大了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是個好女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿的什麼衣服?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她夏天經常穿的白色連衣裙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼不是為了實現願望回來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拼命地認真思考的 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我回去了  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯輪到我來做了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯?現在還沒到中午啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 難道是咖喱?要慢慢煮上八個小時的咖喱?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁太 我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了的面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得好早啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?啊 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 今天只有開學典禮 很快就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著上了節家務課
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 居然搞得這麼亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓 快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別推我啊 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 有那個沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒸麵包 大家都很想吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太君?喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是仁太的媽媽做的好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為沒有葡萄乾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會多多練習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出更更好吃的給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更...你打算一直留在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不行...啊 對了 你去過波波那裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?我不知道啊 面碼一直都在家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他說看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個是面碼的幽靈?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本間芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法和你溝通...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈就幽靈 管它是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面還有雞蛋殼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?唔...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定嗎 我還有事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川是...波波?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你們還交換郵件地址了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現面碼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是選禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羡慕啊 你的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多別的種類的 請慢慢看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是叫我陪你來買 你到底是買給誰的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
