Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫絕對 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起就是說...
