Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要召喚面碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照鬼故事來說的話我覺得應該需要這種小道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 thankyou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 BBQ的材料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我晚上不怎麼吃東西的 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 鶴子只考慮自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:17:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性的女人我可是相當喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得吃的東西大家會帶來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕帶重複了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了這個!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫基魯 這是我在印度吃過的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用牛奶和米煮成的甜粥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好像嘔出來的一樣  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 這也不能算是BBQ啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要我把這個做成鐵板燒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃德國香腸好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 終於著了 沒有火怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 居然來了這麼多人 都過去這麼多年了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹是怎麼切成的來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru還會做螃蟹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和木炭一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木炭不是木頭燒成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難點著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一想起自己曾經是木頭 就會一口氣燒起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是個恰當的比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要我幫你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 你去BBQ吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只有德國香腸 我都已經切好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色連衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 面碼總是穿著的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子說的沒錯 我太容易受別人影響
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是 現在也是 一點沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很像面碼穿的那個 不過面碼又不穿這麼短的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然高中的朋友會穿 可她們肯定不穿白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實也是自己考慮過後才穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實有時候很沒主見 其實我自己也考慮了很多...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些話 對我說了有什麼用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是這樣啊 真了不起」你想聽我這樣說嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概...是希望你能罵醒總是隨波逐流的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...看啊仁太 變成螃蟹了變成螃蟹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃 純正德國味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!你也吃得出嗎 鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的假的  -對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:49.00,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 螃蟹先生要糊了要糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也能算是甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 面碼的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你也會幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我也信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你肯幫忙嗎 不愧是鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太 看來超和平bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超和平busters最高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超和平...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒聽到這個名字了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-亂說什麼 大家都還是現役的哦  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大家都這麼懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼說不定也會很懷念 突然跑到我們面前來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 就這樣歡迎我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 是雪集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是安城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿來了蔬菜和肉排
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有香料鹽和橄欖油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:07.79,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.12,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是和那些派不上用場的女人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是嚇了我一跳 我還以為是面碼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼我看到了哦 剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪啊 面碼在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那片草地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 走了 仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不只是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到面碼的